<hymn_number>94</hymn_number>
<title>yé sū, wǒ men tóng shēng shuō ài nǐ 迦南94</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 yé sū! yé sū! wǒ men tóng shēng shuō ài nǐ,
 yé sū! yé sū! wǒ men qí shēng gē sòng nǐ,
 yīn nǐ ràng wǒ men kuài lè, ràng wǒ men tóng xīn hé yì,
 zài méi yǒu, zài méi yǒu, bǐ nǐ gèng hǎo gèng měi.</lyrics>
</song>